attributes.review: I was casually strolling down the street, when out popped a man that resembled a pasty white tapeworm. He asked me to take him to my place of work. I hesitated, but reluctantly agreed. As we arrived, I asked him which treatment he would like to receive. He said he would like the most expensive option. I pulled out the darkest shade and began to apply the tanning lotion to this man. After I was finished, he no longer resembled a tapeworm, but rather, a dusty stale Cheeto that had been stepped on and then sweeped into cat throw up.
